<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><map display_value="Urgent Incident Conf Trigger TF">74c8bdcc0f1f71002a14c19ce1050e46</map><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[/*globals, SNC, NotifyNow*/

/**
 * Created by bryan.barnard on 4/6/15.
 * Transform Map Script to initiate or terminate conf call for K15 Demo
 */
(function () {
    var logSrc = 'K15_API_DEMO';

    var kickAllFromConference = function () {
        var nn = new SNC.NotifyNow(),
            table = 'notifynow_participant',
            queryString = 'active=true',
            participantRecords = new GlideRecord(table);


        // get current conference call participants
        participantRecords.addQuery(queryString);
        participantRecords.query();


        // kick all active conf call participants
        while (participantRecords.next()) {
            if (participantRecords.isValid()) {
                nn.kick(participantRecords);
            }
        }
    };


    var initializeConference = function () {

        var participants = [],
            table = 'u_session_attendees',
            limit = 20,
            participantRecords = new GlideRecord(table);



        // get participants for notification
        participantRecords.setLimit(limit);
        participantRecords.addNotNullQuery('u_e_164');
        participantRecords.query();


        // iterate participant records getting E.164 validated phone number
        while (participantRecords.next()) {
            participants.push(participantRecords.getValue('u_e_164'));

            gs.log('adding participant: ' + participantRecords.getValue('u_e_164'), logSrc);
        }


        // initiate conference call
        var nn = new SNC.NotifyNow();
        var cc = nn.initiateConferenceCall(participants, "K15 API DEMO");
        gs.log('started conference call: ' + cc.getUniqueValue() + ' and code: ' + cc.getValue('code'), logSrc);
    };


    // main
    if (source.u_action == 'kick') {
        gs.log('attempting to kick all participants from call', logSrc);
        kickAllFromConference();
    } else {
        gs.log('attempting to initialize conference call with registered attendees', logSrc);
        initializeConference();
    }

})();

var initializeConferenceCall = function() {
    // initialize participants array
    var participants = [];

    // get all conference call participants
    var records = new GlideRecord('u_session_attendees');
    records.addNotNullQuery('u_e_164');
    records.query();

    // iterate over participant records
    while (records.next()) {
        // get the value of the E.164 Phone Number field and add
        // it to the participant array
        participants.push(records.getValue('u_e_164'));

        gs.log('adding participant: ' + records.getValue('u_e_164'));
    }

    // initiate conference call
    var nn = new SNC.NotifyNow();
    var cc = nn.initiateConferenceCall(participants, 'test with ' + participants.length + ' participants');

    gs.log('started conference call: ' + cc.getUniqueValue() + ' and code: ' + cc.getValue('code'));
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-04-06 22:41:52</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>5f6182850f93b1002a14c19ce1050e5b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onAfter</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_5f6182850f93b1002a14c19ce1050e5b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-04-14 15:12:31</sys_updated_on><when>onAfter</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>
